\[\|\tilde{\chi}_{g}\|\|\chi_{g}^{-1}\|\cdot\frac{\|f(\tilde{x}+\tilde{h},z)-f( \tilde{x},z)-D_{x}f(\tilde{x},z)\tilde{h}\|}{\|\tilde{h}\|}\]

