\[\langle f,(M_{g}\#\mu)^{G}\rangle=\int_{G}\langle f,M_{h}\#(M_{g}\#\mu) \rangle d\lambda_{G}(h)=\int_{G}\langle f,(M_{\tilde{h}})\#\mu\rangle d \lambda_{G}(\tilde{h})=\langle f,\mu^{G}\rangle,\]

